									"patching_rect" : [ 10.0, 120.0, 412.0, 97.0 ],
									"text" : "Drag individual soundfiles, or a folder of soundfiles, into the scrubbing area.\nThen click-scrub the mouse across the area, using various gestures. The soundfiles will be played back in rapid succession, overalapping to form dense textures.\n\nEach 'track' in the scrubbing window goes from low pitch (bottom) to high pitch (top). Pitch shifting is achieved by simple 'varispeed' transposition, so lower sounds last longer.\n\nLeft to right across the 'track' pans the sounds's starting position around the eight channels. The sounds do not move once they are playing"
								}

